quran[83]{c,v,t}:
  36,1,(ys) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  36,2,"yqsm allah taealaa bialquran almhkm bma fih min al'ahkam walhukm walhjj, 'iinak -ayha alrswl- lamin almursalin bwhy allah 'iilaa ebadh, ealaa tariq mustaqim metdl, wahu al'islam"
  36,3,"yqsm allah taealaa bialquran almhkm bma fih min al'ahkam walhukm walhjj, 'iinak -ayha alrswl- lamin almursalin bwhy allah 'iilaa ebadh, ealaa tariq mustaqim metdl, wahu al'islam"
  36,4,"yqsm allah taealaa bialquran almhkm bma fih min al'ahkam walhukm walhjj, 'iinak -ayha alrswl- lamin almursalin bwhy allah 'iilaa ebadh, ealaa tariq mustaqim metdl, wahu al'islam"
  36,5,"hdha alquran tanzil aleaziz fi antqamh min 'ahl alkufr walmeasy, alrahim biman tab min eibadih waeamil salhana"
  36,6,"anzlnah ealayk -ayha alrswl- lthdhr bih qwmana lm yundhar abawuhum min qblk, wahum alerb, fhwla' alqawm sahun ean al'iiman walastqamt ealaa aleamal alsalh. wakulu 'umat ynqte eanha al'iindhar taqae fi alghflt, wafi hdha dalil ealaa wjwb aldaewat waltdhkyr ealaa aleulama' biallah wshreh; l'iyqaz almuslimin min ghflthm"
  36,7,"lqd wjb aleadhab ealaa 'akthar hwla' alkafryn, baed 'an eurid ealayhim alhaqu frfdwh, fahum la yusadiqun biallah wala brswlh, wala yaemalun bshreh"
  36,8,"'iinaa jaealna hwla' alkufaar aladhin eurd ealayhim alhaqu frdduh, wasrru ealaa alkufr wedm al'iyman, kaman jueil fi 'aenaqihim aghlal, fjmet 'aydihim mae 'aenaqihim taht adhqanhm, fadtru 'iilaa rafe rwwshm 'iilaa alsma', fahum mghlwlwn ean kl khyr, la yubsirun alhaqi wala yahtadun 'ilyh"
  36,9,"wjelna min 'amam alkafirin sddana wamin warayihim sddana, fahum bmnzlt min sudd tariqah min bayn yadayh wamin khlfh, faemyna absarhm; bsbb kufruhum wastkbarhm, fahum la yubsirun rshdana, wala yhtdwn. wakulun min qabil daewatan al'islam bal'ierad walenad, fahu haqiq bhdha aleqab"
  36,10,"ystwy eind hwla' alkufaar almeandyn thdhyrk lahum -ayha alrswl- wedm thdhyrk, fahum la ysddiqwn wala yemlwn"
  36,11,"'inma yanfae thdhyrk man aman balqran, watabie ma fih min 'ahkam allh, wakhaf alrhmn, hayth la yarah 'ahad 'iilaa allh, fbshshirh bimaghfirat min allah ldhnwbh, wthwab minh fi alakhirat ealaa 'aemalah alsalht, wahu dukhulih aljnt"
  36,12,"'ina nahn nuhyi al'amwat jmyeana bbethhm yawm alqyamt, wanaktub ma eamiluu min alkhayr walshr, watharahum alty kanuu sbbana fiha fi hayatihim wabaed mmathm min khyr, kalwld alsalh, walealam alnafe, walsdqt aljaryt, wamin shr, kalshrk walesyan, wkll shay' 'ahsaynah fi kitab wadih hu amm alktb, wa'iilayh mrjeha, wahu allwh almhfwz. faealaa aleaql muhasabatan nfsh; liakun qudwatan fi alkhayr fi hayatah wabaed mmath"
  36,13,"wadrb -ayha alrswl- lmshrky qawmak alraddin ldewtk mathalaan yaetabirun bh, wahu qisat 'ahl alqryt, hin dhahab 'iilayhim almrslwn, 'iidh 'arsalna 'iilayhim rswlyn ldewthm 'iilaa al'iiman biallah wtrk eibadat ghyrh, fkdhdhab 'ahl alqaryat alrswlyn, fezzaznahma wqwynahma birasul thalth, faqal althlatht li'ahl alqryt: 'iinaa 'iilaykum -ayha alqwm- mrslwn"
  36,14,"wadrib -ayha alrswl- lmshrky qawmak alraddin ldewtk mathalaan yaetabirun bh, wahu qisat 'ahl alqryt, hin dhahab 'iilayhim almrslwn, 'iidh 'arsalna 'iilayhim rswlyn ldewthm 'iilaa al'iiman biallah wtrk eibadat ghyrh, fkdhdhab 'ahl alqaryat alrswlyn, fezzaznahma wqwynahma birasul thalth, faqal althlatht li'ahl alqryt: 'iinaa 'iilaykum -ayha alqwm- mrslwn"
  36,15,"qal 'ahl alqaryat llmrslyn: ma 'antum 'iilaa 'unas mthlna, wama 'unzil alrhmn shyyana min alwhy, wama 'antum -ayha alrsl- 'iilaa tkdhbwn"
  36,16,"qal almursalun mwkdyn: rbbuna aladhi 'arsalna yaelam 'iinaa 'iilaykum lmrslwn, wama ealayna 'illa tblygh alrisalat bwdwh, wala namlik hdaytkm, falhdayt biad allah whdh"
  36,17,"qal almursalun mwkdyn: rbbuna aladhi 'arsalna yaelam 'iinaa 'iilaykum lmrslwn, wama ealayna 'illa tblygh alrisalat bwdwh, wala namlik hdaytkm, falhdayt biad allah whdh"
  36,18,"qal 'ahl alqryt: 'iinaa tasha'amna bkm, layin lam tkuffu ean daeawtukum lana lnqtlnkm rmyana balhjart, wlysybnkm mnna eadhab 'alim mwje"
  36,19,"qal almrslwn: shwmkm waemalkm min alshirk walshr maeakum wmrdwdt elykm, a'in wueztm bma fyh khyrkm tsha'mtm wtwedtmwna balrjm waltedhyb? bal 'antum qawm eadtkm al'israf fi aleisyan waltkdhyb"
  36,20,"wja' min makan baeid fi almadinat rajul msre (wdhlk hin ealim 'ana 'ahl alqaryat hammu biqatl alrusul 'aw tedhybhm), qal: ya qawm atabieuu almursalin 'iilaykum min allh, atabaeuu aldhyn la yatlubun minkum 'amwalana ealaa 'iiblagh alrsalt, wahum muhtadun fima ydewnkm 'iilayh min eibadat allah whdh. wafi hdha bayan fadl man saeaa 'iilaa al'amr bialmaeruf walnhy ean almnkr"
  36,21,"waja' min makan baeid fi almadinat rajul msre (wdhlk hin ealim 'ana 'ahl alqaryat hammu biqatl alrusul 'aw tedhybhm), qal: ya qawm atabieuu almursalin 'iilaykum min allh, atabaeuu aldhyn la yatlubun minkum 'amwalana ealaa 'iiblagh alrsalt, wahum muhtadun fima ydewnkm 'iilayh min eibadat allah whdh. wafi hdha bayan fadl man saeaa 'iilaa al'amr bialmaeruf walnhy ean almnkr"
  36,22,"way shay' ymneny min 'an 'aebud allah aladhi khlqny, wa'iilayh tsyrwn jmyeana?"
  36,23,"aaebd min dun allah alihatan 'ukhraa la tamlik min al'amr shyyana, 'iina yrdny alrhmn bisu' fhdhh alalihat la tamlik dafe dhlk wala mneh, wala tastatie 'inqadhy mimaa 'ana fyh? 'iiniy 'iina faealt dhlk lafi khataan wadih zahr. 'iiniy amant birabikum fastamieuu 'iilaa ma qulth lkm, watyewny bal'iyman. falamaa qal dhlk wthb 'iilayh qawmih wqtlwh, fadkhlh allah aljnt"
  36,24,"aaebd min dun allah alihatan 'ukhraa la tamlik min al'amr shyyana, 'iina yrdny alrhmn bisu' fhdhh alalihat la tamlik dafe dhlk wala mneh, wala tastatie 'inqadhy mimaa 'ana fyh? 'iiniy 'iina faealt dhlk lafi khataan wadih zahr. 'iiniy amant birabikum fastamieuu 'iilaa ma qulth lkm, watyewny bal'iyman. falamaa qal dhlk wthb 'iilayh qawmih wqtlwh, fadkhlh allah aljnt"
  36,25,"aaebd min dun allah alihatan 'ukhraa la tamlik min al'amr shyyana, 'iina yrdny alrhmn bisu' fhdhh alalihat la tamlik dafe dhlk wala mneh, wala tastatie 'inqadhy mimaa 'ana fyh? 'iiniy 'iina faealt dhlk lafi khataan wadih zahr. 'iiniy amant birabikum fastamieuu 'iilaa ma qulth lkm, watyewny bal'iyman. falamaa qal dhlk wthb 'iilayh qawmih wqtlwh, fadkhlh allah aljnt"
  36,26,"qyl lah baed qtlh: 'udkhil aljnt, 'ikramana lh"
  36,27,"qal wahu fi alnaeim walkramt: ya layt qawmi yaelamun bghfran rabiy li w'ikramh 'iyay; bsbb 'iymany biallah wsbry ealaa taeth, waitibae rusulah hataa qutilt, fayuminuu biallah fydkhlu aljanat mthly"
  36,28,"wama aihtaj al'amr 'iilaa 'iinzal jund min alsama' ledhabhm baed qatlahum alrajul alnash lahum wtkdhybhm rslhm, fahum 'adeaf min dhlk wahwn, wama kunaa munzilin almalayikat ealaa al'umam 'iidha ahlknahm, bal nabeath ealayhim edhabana ydmrhm"
  36,29,"ma kan hlakhm 'iilaa bsyht wahdt, fa'iidha hum mayitun lm tabq minhum baqyt"
  36,30,"ya hasratan aleabbad wndamthm yawm alqiamat 'iidha eaynu aledhab, ma yatihim min rasul min allah taealaa 'iilaa kanuu bih yastahziuwn wyskhrwn"
  36,31,alm yar hwla' almsthzywn wyetbru biman qablahum min alqurun alty 'ahlaknaha 'anahum la yarjieun 'iilaa hadhih aldyna?
  36,32,"wma kl hadhih alqurun alty 'ahlaknaha wghyrhm, 'iilaa muhdarun jmyeana eindana yawm alqiamat llhsab waljza'"
  36,33,"wdlalt lhwla' almushrikin ealaa qudrat allah ealaa albaeth walnshwr: hadhih al'ard almaytat alty la naba'at fyha, 'ahyaynaha b'inzal alma', wa'akhrajna minha 'anwae alnbat mimaa yakul alnaas walaneam, wamin 'ahya al'ard balnbat 'ahya alkhalq baed almmat"
  36,34,"wjelna fi hadhih al'ard basatin min nakhil waenab, wfjjarna fiha min euyun almiah ma ysqyha"
  36,35,"kl dhlk; lyakl aleabbad min thmrh, wama dhlk 'iilaa min rahmat allah bihim la bseyhm wala bkddihm, wala bhwlhm wbqwthm, 'afala yashkurun allah ealaa ma 'aneam bih ealayhim min hadhih alnaeam alty la tedd wala thsa?"
  36,36,"tnzzah allah aleazim aladhi khalaq al'asnaf jmyeha min 'anwae naba'at alard, wamin 'anfusihim dhkwrana w'inathana, wamimaa la yaelamun min mkhlwqat allah alakhra. qad ainfarad subhanah balkhlq, fala ynbghy 'an yushrak bih ghyrh"
  36,37,"welamt lahum dalt ealaa tawhid allah wkmal qdrth: hdha allayl nnze minh alnhar, fa'iidha alnaas mzlmwn"
  36,38,"wayt lahum alshams tajri limustaqarin lha, qddarh allah laha la ttedah wala tqsr enh, dhlk taqdir aleaziz aldhy la yghalab, alealim aldhy la yaghib ean ealamah shy'"
  36,39,"walqmr ayatan fi khlqh, qddarnah manazil kl lylt, yabda hlala dyyla hataa yukmil qmrana mstdyrana, thuma yarjie dyyla mithl eidhq alnakhlat almtqws fi alrqt walanhna' walsfrt; lqdmh wyubsh"
  36,40,"lkl min alshams walqamar wallayl walnahar waqt qddarh allah lah la yteddah, fala yumkin lilshams 'an tulhiq alqamar ftmhw nwrh, 'aw tughayir mjrah, wala yumkin lllayl 'ana yasbiq alnhar, fydkhl ealayh qabl anqda' wqth, wakulun min alshams walqamar walkwakb fi falak yajrwn"
  36,41,"wdlyl lahum wbrhan ealaa 'ana allah wahdah almsthq llebadt, almuneim balnem, anna hamalna man naja min walad adam fi safinat nuh almmlw't bajnas almkhlwqat; liaistimrar alhayat baed altwfan"
  36,42,wkhlqna lhwla' almushrikin wghyrhm mithl safinat nuh min alsufun wghyrha min almarakib alty yrkbwnha wtbllighhm awtanhm
  36,43,"w'in nasha nghrqhm, fala yajidun mghythana lahum min ghrqhm, wala hum ykhlswn min alghrq"
  36,44,'ila 'ana nrhmhm fnnjyhm wnmtehm 'iilaa ajl; laealahum yarjieun wystdrkwn ma frratu fyh
  36,45,"w'idha qil llmshrkyn: ahdhru 'amr alakhirat wahwalha wahwal aldunya weqabha; raja' rahmat allah lkm, aerdu, walam yujibuu 'iilaa dhlk"
  36,46,"wma tjy' hwla' almushrikin min elamt wadihatan min eind rbhm; lthdyhm llhq, wtbyin lahum sidq alrswl, 'iilaa 'aeraduu enha, walam yntfeu bha"
  36,47,"w'idha qil llkafryn: 'anfaquu min alrizq aldhy mann bih allah elykm, qaluu lilmuminin muhtjjin: 'anuteim man law sha' allah atemh? ma 'antum -ayha almwmnwn- 'illa fi bued wadih ean alhq, 'iidh tamurunana bdhlk"
  36,48,"wyqwl hwla' alkufaar ealaa wajh altkdhyb walastejal: mataa yakun albaeth 'iin kuntum sadiqin fima tqwlwnh enh?"
  36,49,"ma yantazir hwla' almushrikun aladhin yastaejilun bweyd allah 'iiahum 'iilaa nafkhat alfazae eind qiam alsaet, takhudhuhum fjat, wahum yakhtasimun fi shuuwn hyathm"
  36,50,"fala yastatie hwla' almushrikun eind alnfkh fi \"alqrn\" 'ana ywsu ahdana bshy', wala yastatieun alrujue 'iilaa ahlhm, bal yamutun fi aswaqhm wmwadehm"
  36,51,"wnufikh fi \"alqrn\" alnfkht althanyt, fturadd arwahhm 'iilaa ajsadhm, fa'iidha hum min qbwrhm yakhrujun 'iilaa rabihim sraeana"
  36,52,"qal almukadhibun balbeth nadmyn: ya hlakna man 'ukhrijna min qbwrna? fyjabwn wyqal lhm: hdha maa waead bih alrhmn, wakhbr eanh almursalun alsadqwn"
  36,53,"ma kan albaeth min alqubur 'iilaa natijat nafkhat wahidat fi \"alqrn\", fa'iidha jmye alkhalq ladayna mathlwn llhsab waljza'"
  36,54,"fy dhlk alyawm ytm alhisab baledl, fala tuzlm nafs shyyana bnqs hsnatha 'aw ziadat syyatha, wala tujzwn 'iilaa bima kuntum temlwnh fi aldnya"
  36,55,'in 'ahl aljanat fi dhalik alyawm mshghwlwn ean ghyrhm bi'anwae alnaeim alty ytfkhwn bha
  36,56,"hm wa'azwajihim mtnemwn baljlws ealaa alasrrat almzyant, taht alzilal alwarft"
  36,57,"lhm fi aljanat 'anwae alfwakh alldhydht, walahum kl ma yatlubun min 'anwae alneym"
  36,58,"wlhm naeim akhar 'akbar hin yukalimuhum rbhm, alrahim bihim bialsalam elyhm. waeind dhlk tahsul lahum alsalamat alttamat min jmye alwjwh"
  36,59,"wyqal llkfar fi dhalik alywm: tmyazu ean almwmnyn, wanfslu enhm"
  36,60,"wyqwl allah lahum twbykhana wtdhkyrana: 'alam awskm ealaa alsnt rusuli 'an laa taebuduu alshaytan wala ttyewh? 'iinah lakum eaduun zahir aledawt"
  36,61,"wamrtkm bebadty whdy, febadty wtaety wmesyt alshaytan hi aldiyn alqwym almawsil lmrdaty wjnnaty"
  36,62,"wlqd adll alshaytan ean alhaqu minkum khlqana kthyrana, 'afama kan lakum eaql -ayha almshrkwn- yanhakum ean atbaeh?"
  36,63,hdhh jahanam alati kuntum tueadun biha fi aldunya ealaa kfrkm biallah wtkdhybkm rslh
  36,64,adkhlwha alyawm wqasu hrraha; bsbb kfrkm
  36,65,"alyawm natbae ealaa afwah almushrikin fala yntqwn, wtukllimna 'aydihim bima btsht bh, watashhad 'arjuluhum bima saeat 'iilayh fi aldnya, wksbt min alatham"
  36,66,"wlw nasha' latamasna ealaa 'aeyunuhum bi'ana nudhhb absarhm, kama khtmna ealaa afwahhm, fbadaru 'iilaa alsirat lyjwzwh, fkyf yatahaqaq lahum dhlk waqad tumist absarhm?"
  36,67,"wlw shina laghayarna khalaqahum waqednahm fi amaknhm, fala yastatieun 'an yamdu amamhm, wala yrjeu wra'hm"
  36,68,"wmn nutil eumruh hataa yhrm nueidh 'iilaa alhalat alty abtda minha halat daef aleaql wadief aljsd, 'afala yaeqilun ann man faeal mithl hdha bihim qadir ealaa bethhm?"
  36,69,"wma ellamna rasulina mhmdana alsher, wama yanbaghi lah 'an yakun shaerana, ma hdha aladhi ja' bih 'iilaa dhikr yatadhakar bih 'uwlu alalbab, waquran byin aldlalt ealaa alhaqi walbatl, wadihatan ahkamh whikamh wmwaezh; liyundhir man kan hy alqalb mstnyr albsyrt, wayuhiqu aleadhab ealaa alkafirin ballh; li'anahum qamat ealayhim bialquran hujat allah albalght"
  36,70,"wma ellamna rasulina mhmdana alsher, wama yanbaghi lah 'an yakun shaerana, ma hdha aladhi ja' bih 'iilaa dhikr yatadhakar bih 'uwlu alalbab, waquran byin aldlalt ealaa alhaqi walbatl, wadihatan ahkamh whikamh wmwaezh; liyundhir man kan hy alqalb mstnyr albsyrt, wayuhiqu aleadhab ealaa alkafirin ballh; li'anahum qamat ealayhim bialquran hujat allah albalght"
  36,71,"awlm yar alkhalq 'anaa khalaqna lajlhm aneamana dhllnaha lhm, fahum malikun amrha?"
  36,72,"wskhkharnaha lhm, faminha ma yarkabun fi alasfar, wayahmilun ealayha alathqal, waminha ma yaklwn"
  36,73,"wlhm fiha manafie 'ukhraa yntfewn bha, kalantfae baswafha wa'awbariha wa'asheariha athathana wlbasana, waghayr dhlk, wyshrbwn albanha, 'afala yashkurun allah aladhi 'aneam ealayhim bhdhh alnem, wykhlswn lah alebad?"
  36,74,waitakhadh almushrikun min dun allah alihatan yebdwnha; tmeana fi nsrha lahum w'inqadhhm min eadhab allh
  36,75,"la tastatie tilk alalihat nasr eabdyha wala 'anfusahum ynsrwn, walmshrkwn walhthm jmyeana muhdarun fi aledhab, mtbry baeduhum min bed"
  36,76,"fla yahzunk -ayha alrswl- kufruhum biallah wtkdhybhm lak wasthzawhm bk; 'iinaa naelam ma ykhfwn, wama yzhrwn, wsnjazyhm ealaa dhlk"
  36,77,"awlm yar al'iinsan almunkar llbeth aibtida'an khalaqah fystdl bih ealaa meadh, 'anaa khalaqnah min nutfat mrrat batwar hataa kabir, fa'iidha hu kthyr alkhisam wadih aljdal?"
  36,78,"wdrb lana almunkar llbeth mathalaan laa yanbaghi drbh, wahu qyas qudrat alkhaliq bqdrt almkhlwq, wanasi aibtida'an khlqh, qal: man yuhyi aleizam albalyt almtftt?"
  36,79,"ql lh: yuhyiha aladhi khalaqaha 'awal mrt, wahu bjmye khalaqah elym, la yakhfaa ealayh shy'"
  36,80,"aldhy 'akhraj lakum min alshajar al'akhdar alrtb narana mhrqt, fa'iidha 'antum min alshajar tuqidun alnar, fahu alqadir ealaa 'iikhraj aldd min aldd. wafi dhlk dalil ealaa whdanyt allah wkmal qdrth, wamin dhlk 'iikhraj almawtaa min qbwrhm ahya'"
  36,81,"awlys aladhi khalaq alsmwat wal'ard wama fihima biqadir ealaa 'an yakhluq mthlhm, fyeydhm kama bdahm? bla، 'iinah qadir ealaa dhlk, wahu alkhalaaq lajamie almkhlwqat, alealim bikuli ma khalaq wyakhluqu, la yakhfaa ealayh shy'"
  36,82,"'inma 'amrih subhanah wteala 'iidha 'arad shyyana 'an yaqul lh: \"kn\" fykwn, wamin dhlk al'imatt wal'ihya', walbeth walnshwr"
  36,83,"ftnzh allah taealaa wtqds ean aleajz walshrk, fahu almalk likuli shy', almtsrf fi shuuwn khalaqah bila mnaze 'aw mmane, waqad zaharat dalayil qdrth, wtmam nemth, wa'iilayh turjewn llhsab waljza'"